headline: Citigroup Stock Has Lost 16% in the Market Sell-Off. Is It a Buy?
summary: Dropping alongside the index were the shares of Citigroup (NYSE: C).  The big difference between the two sell-offs, however, was that Citigroup fell about twice as much as the S&P 500 index.  Does Citigroup's sell-off make it a buy today?
